ms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20upgraded%20my%20Amtrak%20seat%20to%20a%2023-square-foot%20roomette%20by%20bidding%20%24110.%20Here's%20what%20the%2015-hour%20train%20ride%20was%20like.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amtrak%20Pacific%20Surfliner%20train%20passing%20through%20San%20Clemente%20Train%20Station%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c841022a1e600018b898bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20an%20upgrade%2C%20I%20spent%2015%20hours%20in%20a%20roomette%20aboard%20Amtrak's%20Lake%20Shore%20Limited.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-improve-long-train-rides-tips-frequent-amtrak-traveler%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupgraded%20my%20coach%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20a%20private%20roomette%20on%20Amtrak's%20Lake%20Shore%20Limited%20for%20an%20extra%20%24110.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2023-square-foot%20space%20had%20two%20seats%2C%20an%20in-room%20toilet%2C%20a%20foldable%20sink%2C%20and%20a%20tray%20table.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20roomette%20gave%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20privacy%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20share%20one%20with%20another%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20originally%20planned%20to%20travel%20in%20coach%20on%20Amtrak's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amtrak.com%2Flake-shore-limited-train%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELake%20Shore%20Limited%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20my%2015-hour%20trip%20from%20Cleveland%2C%20Ohio%2C%20to%20Pittsfield%2C%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20enjoyed%20traveling%20in%20this%20section%20of%20the%20train%20during%20past%20trips.%20Coach%20tickets%20are%20budget-friendly%2C%20the%20baggage%20allowance%20is%20generous%2C%20the%20seats%20are%20comfortable%2C%20and%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20sells%20snacks%20and%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20this%20trip%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20to%20upgrade%20my%20ticket%20with%20a%20bid%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20getting%20the%20upgrade%20and%20taking%20the%20ride%20was%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmtrak%20passengers%20can%20bid%20to%20upgrade%20their%20tickets%2C%20and%20my%20%24110%20offer%20scored%20me%20a%20roomette.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20door%20leading%20into%20the%20%26quot%3BSleeping%20car%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20Amtrak%20train.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bc774823f362001987856b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Amtrak%20sleeping%20car.%3Cp%3EiStock%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%20Plus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20upgraded%20my%20ticket%20through%20Amtrak's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amtrak.com%2Fbidup%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBidUp%20program%3C%2Fa%3E.%20About%2037%20hours%20before%20my%20trip%2C%20Amtrak%20provided%20a%20price%20range%20for%20bids%20and%20asked%20how%20much%20I'd%20like%20to%20wager%20for%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20traveling%20in%20coach%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20bid%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-business-class-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness-class%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20roomette%2C%20or%20a%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20wagering%20%24110%2C%20the%20minimum%20bid%20I%20could%20place%20on%20a%20roomette%2C%20I%20received%20an%20email%20telling%20me%20that%20Amtrak%20had%20accepted%20it%20and%20upgraded%20my%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20%24226%20on%20my%20trip%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20%24110%20I%20paid%20for%20the%20upgrade.%20If%20I'd%20booked%20a%20roomette%20initially%20instead%20of%20upgrading%2C%20I%20would've%20likely%20paid