C%20and%20boba%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-into-tiny-house-became-minimalist-declutter-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20pretty%20minimally%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20design.%20My%20living%20room%20doubles%20as%20both%20my%20workspace%20and%20hobby%20area%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20owning%20a%20TV%2C%20I%20just%20use%20my%20computer%20since%20I%20rarely%20watch%20television.%20I%20also%20don't%20host%20people%20often%2C%20so%20I've%20never%20felt%20much%20pressure%20to%20furnish%20the%20apartment%20beyond%20the%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20bedroom%20setup%20is%20similarly%20simple%3A%20a%20bed%2C%20a%20blanket%2C%20a%20pillow%2C%20and%20a%20filing%20cabinet%20that%20doubles%20as%20a%20nightstand.%20One%20thing%20I%20did%20splurge%20on%2C%20though%2C%20was%20a%20%24400%20bidet%2C%20which%20felt%20worth%20it%20as%20a%20quality-of-life%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221654%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raymond%20Zeng%20is%20looking%20over%20his%20bed%20in%20his%20minimally%20furnished%20bedroom.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f13ce7ff506e273e660fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZeng's%20bedroom%20is%20also%20minimally%20furnished.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20live%20without%20a%20car%2C%20which%20keeps%20my%20transportation%20costs%20extremely%20low.%20Most%20months%2C%20I%20spend%20little%20to%20nothing%20getting%20around%2C%20though%20occasionally%20I'll%20spend%20about%20%2430%20on%20rideshares%20or%20public%20transit.%20Otherwise%2C%20I'll%20walk%20or%20use%20my%20company's%20shuttle%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20keep%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-food-pyramid-diet-guidelines-experience-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20spending%20modest%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20I%20spend%20around%20%24300%20a%20month%20on%