hat%20would%20have%20been%20over%20%245%2C000%20in%20airfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20discretionary%20spending%20also%20goes%20toward%20the%20furry%20community%2C%20where%20I%20design%20characters%2C%20commission%20artwork%2C%20and%20attend%20conventions%20with%20the%20same%20friends%20I%20spend%20time%20with%20in%20VR.%20The%20community%20centers%20around%20anthropomorphized%20personas%20that%20people%20identify%20with%20and%20use%20as%20creative%20avatars.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20an%20outlet%20for%20self-expression%20that's%20hard%20to%20find%20in%20my%20day%20job%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raymond%20Zeng%20in%20costume.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f1411b1025a62a5c858f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZeng's%20%26quot%3Bfursona%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20robot-dog-like%20creature.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Raymond%20Zeng%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20saving%20up%20for%20a%20custom%20fursuit%2C%20which%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%247%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20luxury%20I%20prioritize%20is%20living%20alone.%20I%20know%20I%20could%20save%20more%20money%20with%20roommates%2C%20but%20having%20my%20own%20space%20is%20worth%20the%20tradeoff%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225674f04b-232c-4b26-8b71-5af9b23b5f99%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20track%20my%20money%20and%20invest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20stock%20vesting%2C%20bonuses%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fttec-pauses-401k-contributions-benefit-cuts-consulting-deloitte-zoom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20contributions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20save%20anywhere%20from%20%245%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20max%20out%20my%20401(k)%2C%20Roth%20IRA%2C%20and%20health%20savings%20account%20every%20year%2C%20and%