0changer'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779802522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-canada-trade-talks-advance-as-carney-calls-cepa-a-game-changer-126052601580_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20Canada%20have%20reaffirmed%20commitment%20to%20a%20balanced%20and%20ambitious%20CEPA%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20aiming%20to%20raise%20bilateral%20trade%20to%20%2450%20billion%20by%202030%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WFH%20is%20a%20bigger%20driver%20of%20entry-level%20job%20woes%20than%20AI%2C%20researchers%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225477%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20IT%20specialist%20works%20from%20home%20in%20Novi%20Sad%2C%20Serbia%2C%20in%20January%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1574d5b1025a62a5c87229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223651%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERemote%20work%20may%20be%20reshaping%20junior%20hiring%20more%20than%20AI%20is%2C%20researchers%20say.%3Cp%3EMaxim%20Konankov%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20has%20often%20been%20blamed%20for%20a%20slowdown%20in%20junior%20recruiting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20researchers%20said%20remote%20work%20may%20be%20slowing%20entry-level%20hiring%20more%20than%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20remote%20work%20makes%20junior%20employees%20harder%20to%20supervise%20and%20train%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20the%20slowdown%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-changing-entry-level-work-advice-to-succeed-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20widely%20blamed%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20has%20warned%20AI%20could%20wipe%20out%20half%20of%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-anthropic-ceos-ai-junior-roles-hiring-davos-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20white-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis%20said%20he%20was%20already%20seeing%20%26quot%3Ba%20slowdown%20in%20hiring%26quot%3B%20for%20junior%20roles%20and%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20two%20researchers%20say%20companies%20may%20actually%20be%20hiring%20fewer%20junior%20workers%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-every-comment-work-from-home-employee-remote-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20them%20harder%20to%20supervise%20and%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20John%20Lambert%2C%20a%20postdoctoral%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20and%20Yannick%20Schindler%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20economist%20at%20the%20Ellison%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20analyzed%20Revelio%20Labs%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20data%20covering%20243%20million%20new%20hires%20and%20Lightcast%20data%20covering%20407%20million%20job%20postings%20across%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Australia%20between%202017%20and%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20conclusion%3A%20work-from-home%20exposure%20was%20a%20much%20stronger%20predictor%20of%20weaker%20junior%20hiring%20than%20generative%20AI%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20point%20strongly%20towards%20WFH%20exposure%20as%20a%20better%20predictor%20of%20the%20decline%20in%20relative%20early-career%20hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22617a7d84-6b50-4afe-b540-4ebe5f72724c%5C%22%3EThe%20WFH%20effect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20challenges%20a%20growing%20body%20of%20research%20suggesting%20ChatGPT%20and%20similar%20AI%20tools%20are%20replacing%20young%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20said%20those%20studies%20may%20have%20confused%20two%20overlapping%20trends.%20Jobs%20most%20exposed%20to%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20including%20software%20developers%2C%20consultants%2C%20accountants%2C%20and%20data%20scientists%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20the%20jobs%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20done%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20researchers%20analyzed%20AI%20exposure%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-driving-us-productivity-boom-stanford-professor-nicholas-bloom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote-work%20exposure%3C%2Fa%3E%20separately%2C%20both%20appeared%20linked%20to%20weaker%20junior%20hiring.%20But%20when%20they%20controlled%20for%20both%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20AI%20effect%20%26quot%3Battenuated%20heavily%20and%20often%20became%20statistically%20indistinguishable%20from%20zero%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20work-from-home%20effect%20remained%20robust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20suggests%20the%20issue%20may%20be%20organizational%20rather%20than%20technological.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWFH%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20raise%20the%20cost%20of%20supervising%20and%20monitoring%20workers%2C%20and%20can%20slow%20on-the-job%20learning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThese%20organizational%20frictions%20can%20erode%20the%20value-proposition%20of%20investing%20in%20early-career%20talent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20still%20reshaping%20entry-level%20work.%20Companies%20are%20increasingly%20using%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20and%20GitHub%20Copilot%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-is-raising-bar-for-entry-level-employees-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautomate%20grunt%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20traditionally%20assigned%20to%20junior%20employees%2C%20pushing%20some%20young%20workers%20into%20higher-level%20responsibilities%20earlier%20in%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263619302-06a2-4b42-a15c-0715c467d2c4%5C%22%3EThe%20junior%20squeeze%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20toward%20remote%20work%20appears%20to%20be%20reshaping%20white-collar%20hiring.%20The%20researchers%20estimate%20that%20by%202025%2C%20occupations%20with%20high%20remote-work%20exposure%20saw%20a%204-to-5%20percentage%20point%20larger%20decline%20in%20junior%20hiring%20than%20less%20remote-friendly%20occupations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20trend%20is%20already%20showing%20up%20in%20federal%20data.%20The%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20recent%20college%20graduates%20stood%20at%205.7%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20compared%20with%204.2%25%20for%20all%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20entry-level%20hiring%20dropped%20sharply%20after%202022%20across%20all%20four%20countries%20analyzed%2C%20with%20US%20entry-level%20hiring%20down%2029%25%20from%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20added%20that%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20AI%20will%20not%20eventually%20disrupt%20labor%20markets.%20Instead%2C%20they%20said%20it%20may%20simply%20be%20too%20early%20to%20conclude%20AI%20is%20already%20replacing%20large%20numbers%20of%20junior%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2C%20as%20our%20results%20indicate%2C%20WFH%20is%20reducing%20the%20incentive%20to%20hire%20junior%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20paper%20concludes%2C%20companies%20may%20need%20to%20rethink%20how%20they%20train%20and%20manage%20young%20employees%20in%20hybrid%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-bigger-driver-entry-level-job-woes-ai-researchers-say-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779802055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1574ecb1025a62a5c8722c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-bigger-driver-entry-level-job-woes-ai-r