chool-raped-screamed-at-denied-food-massive-school-abuse-scandal-in-france-11550212%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-school-monitor-preschool-raped-screamed-at-denied-food-massive-school-abuse-scandal-in-france-11550212%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20to%20Canada%20for%20love%2010%20years%20ago.%20It%20helped%20me%20realize%20which%20friends%20were%20worth%20keeping%20%E2%80%94%20and%20find%20new%20ones.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221338%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20standing%20next%20to%20her%20husband%20near%20the%20water%20with%20the%20Toronto%20skyline%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f12b1b1025a62a5c858cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20met%20my%20now-husband%20on%20a%20dating%20app%20while%20I%20was%20temporarily%20living%20in%20Toronto.%3Cp%3ENaima%20Karp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20temporary%20stint%20in%20Canada%20turned%20into%20a%20permanent%20move%20after%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20my%20now-husband.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficially%20moving%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-toronto-from-nyc-falling-in-love-canada-2025-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20to%20Toronto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20meant%20that%20I%20had%20to%20build%20a%20new%20social%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20put%20myself%20out%20there%20and%20make%20long-lasting%20friendships%20in%20a%20new%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20home%20in%20a%20person%20before%20I%20found%20it%20in%20a%20place.%20In%20January%202017%2C%20I%20met%20my%20now-husband%20%E2%80%94%20a%206-foot-3%20Indo-Fijian%20man%20with%20kind%20eyes%20and%20a%20deep%2C%20soothing%20voice%20%E2%80%94%20on%20Bumble%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20a%20New%20Yorker%20living%20in%20Toronto%20temporarily.%20I%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20childhood%20friends%20in%20the%20city%2C%20and%20I%20was%20bouncing%20between%20Airbnbs%2C%20treating%20Toronto%20as%20a%20short-term%20reset%20to%20help%20me%20heal%20during%20a%20tough%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20looking%20for%20forever%20on%20the%20apps%3A%20just%20casual%20connections%2C%20maybe%20even%20a%20fling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%20City%2C%20I%20had%20always%20felt%20like%20an%20alien%2C%20without%20a%20true%20sense%20of%20belonging.%20Between%20dating%20emotionally%20unavailable%20men%2C%20chronic%20anxiety%2C%20and%20holding%20onto%20friendships%20that%20I'd%20outgrown%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20fully%20found%20my%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20him%2C%20though%2C%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20and%20safe%20immediately.%20Even%20though%20I%20hadn't%20necessarily%20planned%20to%20stay%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20turn%20my%20six-month%20stint%20in%20Toronto%20into%20a%20more%20permanent%20move%20by%20enrolling%20in%20a%20postgrad%20program%20and%20then%20getting%20a%20work%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa6cd58d-1d91-4304-85e4-2beb4994734e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20in%20Canada%20meant%20starting%20over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221796%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20drinking%20wine%20and%20eating%20charcuterie%20with%20a%20friend%20in%20Toronto%2C%20with%20a%20dog%20nearby.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f12ebb1025a62a5c858d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221208%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaking%20my%20first%20real%20friend%20in%20Canada%20helped%20me%20develop%20the%20confidence%20to%20put%20myself%20out%20there%20with%20others.%3Cp%3ENaima%20Karp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20deeply%20in%20love%2C%20but%20the%20harder%20I%20fell%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realized%20how%20alone%20I%20felt%20outside%20our%20relationship.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20experiencing%20a%20love%20that%20felt%20healthy%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20recognize%20what%20I%20needed%20from%20the%20other%20relationships%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20of%20my%20relationships%20that%20weren't%20fulfilling%20those%20needs%20fell%20to%20the%20wayside%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20with%20the%20childhood%20friends%20I'd%20been%20visiting%20in%20Toronto%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20mention%20my%20remaining%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20of%20course%2C%20were%20living%20further%20away%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20my%20partner%20and%20his%20dog%2C%20Diesel%20%E2%80%94%20who%2C%20at%2014%2C%20I%20still%20consider%20one%20of%20my%20best%20friends%20today%20%E2%80%94%20I%20felt%20fully%20and%20truly%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20goal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-making-friends-cooking-hosting-dinner-parties-strangers-new-york-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeeting%20new%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20tried%20taking%20classes%20and%20joining%20workout%20studios.%20The%20women%20seemed%20friendly%2C%20but%20I%20was%20too%20shy%20to%20make%20the%20first%20move%2C%20especially%20when%20many%20showed%20up%20in%20pairs%20or%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20saving%20grace%20was%20my%20friend%20Leila.%20We%20first%20met%20when%20I%20took%20one%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincrease-vo2-max-fitness-class-review-make-cardio-fun-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkout%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20immediately%20found%20her%20empowering%2C%20inclusive%20approach%20to%20movement%20refreshing.%20I%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20interview%20her%20for%20a%20magazine%20I'd%20been%20writing%20for%2C%20and%20she%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chatted%20over%20a%20joint%20in%20a%20park%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20best%20friends%20ever%20since.%20I%20lovingly%20call%20her%20my%20forest%20fairy%2C%20since%20she's%20happiest%20in%20nature%20with%20her%20feet%20in%20the%20mud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeila%20and%20I%20learned%20to%20communicate%20and%20even%20argue%20in%20a%20healthy%2C%20respectful%20way%2C%20brushing%20away%20the%20detritus%20of%20the%20past%20to%20make%20room%20for%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20relationship%20gave%20me%20the%20courage%20to%20make%20the%20first%20move%20with%20others%20and%20to%20embrace%20the%20possibility%20of%20connection%20with%20new%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad20d53e-2011-4569-a179-1403dce77c4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20went%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%20to%20build%20friendships%20with%20intention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20sitting%20on%20a%20brown%20bench%20next%20to%20her%20neighbor%2C%20with%20a%20park%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0f134e51ede568c7e16ef9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20built%20a%20close%20friendship%20with%20my%20neighbor%2C%20Sue.%3Cp%3ENaima%20Karp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20finished%20my%20postgrad%20program%2C%20I'd%20made%20two%20friends%3A%20Pooja%20and%20Anisha.%20I%20was%20guarded%20during%20my%20time%20at%20school%20due%20to%20the%20fallout%20that%20had%20happened%20with%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-closer-to-childhood-friends-surprising-benefits-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echildhood%20group%20of%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20open%20myself%20to%20more%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20knowing%20I%20was%20engaged%20and%20that%20Toronto%20would%20become%20more%20of%20a%20permanent%20home%2C%20I%20challenged%20myself%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforced-myself-say-yes-all-plans-off-phone-made-friends-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esay%20yes%20to%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Pooja%20has%20since%20moved%20back%20to%20India%2C%20Anisha%20and%20I%20still%20regularly%20connect%2C%20checking%20Toronto%20caf%C3%A9s%20off%20our%20bucket%20list%20every%20month%20or%20so.%20Around%20this%20time%2C%20I%20also%20bonded%20with%20my%20neighbor%20Sue%20over%20having%20big%2C%20goofy%20dogs%2C%20and%20discovered%20the%20beauty%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintergenerational-friendship-benefits-fifty-year-difference-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintergenerational%20friendship%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20returned%20to%20the%20Bumble%20app%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%2C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flonely-young-women-bumble-bff-platonic-soulmates-share-bed-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBumble%20BFF%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20helped%20me%20meet%20like-minded%20women%20and%20make%20the%20first%20move.%20As%20an%20introvert%2C%20finding%20people%20with%20similar%20interests%20and%20lifestyles%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20come%20up%20with%20icebreakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20early%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-date-should-always-be-coffee-matchmaker-advice-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20dates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20first%20messages%20have%20since%20grown%20into%20deep%2C%20meaningful%20friendships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244bccdaa-fc4d-45e2-b7e5-b460dae856a7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriendship%20takes%20effort%2C%20and%20when%20it%20pays%20off%2C%20it's%20magic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I've%20been%20in%20Toronto%20for%20almost%2010%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20happily%20married%20to%20my%20husband%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20that%20time%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20learned%20that%20friendships%20can%20build%20slowly%2C%20and%20that%20s