rt-nvidia-microsoft-meta-alphabet-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eview%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20based%20on%20options%20and%20stock%20market%20volume%20as%20well%20as%20fundamentals.%20He%20noted%20that%20trading%20volumes%20of%20Nvidia%20stock%2C%20on%20a%2050-day%20moving%20average%20basis%2C%20are%20at%20their%20%26quot%3Blowest%20since%201999.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bdearth%20of%20hedging%20activity%26quot%3B%20because%20it's%20cheaper%20to%20buy%20put%20options%20on%20Nvidia%20than%20for%20similar%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20does%20fall%2C%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Bvery%20few%20buyers%20on%20the%20way%20down%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20insufficient%20structural%20demand%20and%20market%20makers%20having%20to%20back%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmichaeljburry.substack.com%2Fp%2Fthe-heretics-guide-to-ais-stars-part%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFriday%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Burry%20flagged%20that%20Nvidia's%20customer%20concentration%20is%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20charts%2C%26quot%3B%20exposing%20it%20to%20a%20major%20revenue%20hit%20if%20its%20biggest%20buyers%20pull%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-stock-price-revenue-eps-q1-2027-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecent%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20its%20top%20three%20customers%20were%20responsible%20for%2064%25%20of%20its%20accounts%20receivable%2C%20up%20from%2056%25%20in%20the%20preceding%20quarter%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20its%20No.%201%20customer%20accounted%20for%20more%20of%20Nvidia's%20accounts%20receivable%2C%20but%20less%20of%20its%20revenue%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2013%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20quite%20a%20smoking%20gun%2C%20but%20more%20of%20a%20finding%20of%20a%20finger%20on%20the%20trigger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20suggested%20Microsoft%20pulled%20forward%20inventory%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20really%20need%26quot%3B%20as%20it's%20slowing%20down%20its%20data-center%20buildout%2C%20because%20it%20wanted%20to%20keep%20its%20priority%20spot%20for%20Nvidia's%20next%20chip%2C%20or%20Nvidia%20pushed%20inventory%20forward%20to%20flatter%20its%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bwicked%20bullwhip%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20how%20a%20small%20change%20in%20customer%20demand%20can%20reverberate%20through%20a%20supply%20chain%20and%20have%20a%20more%20pronounced%20effect%20on%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20has%20previously%20said%20he's%20betting%20against%20Nvidia%20and%20other%20high-flying%20AI%20stocks%2C%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-short-michael-burry-nvidia-stock-earnings-ai-bubble-microchips-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%20singled%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20chipmaker%20as%20particularly%20vulnerable%20if%20the%20AI%20boom%20falters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5886db6-7ab6-4002-bce7-8aa1dc24f7a9%5C%22%3EDemand%20is%20set%20to%20slow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20called%20out%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-coo-andrew-macdonald-ai-token-spending-harder-justify-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etokenmaxxing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20companies%20encouraging%20employees%20to%20use%20AI%20models%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%2C%20rushed%2C%20temporary%20phase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTokenmaxxing%20is%20not%20merely%20heavy%20AI%20use%2C%20and%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20sustainable%20AI%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quota-driven%2C%20leaderboard-driven%2C%20management-mandated%20overconsum