interaction%20remains%20crucial%20in%20many%20professions%2C%20suggesting%20the%20employment%20impact%20will%20be%20less%20severe%20than%20initially%20feared.%20Altman%20stated%20he%20doesn't%20foresee%20a%20widespread%20%26quot%3Bjobs%20apocalypse%26quot%3B%20driven%20by%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hot%20new%20AI%20job%20every%20grad%20should%20get%20into%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AI%20chief%20product%20officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jiaona%20Zhang%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a157852b1025a62a5c8723b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJiaona%20Zhang%20is%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20at%20Laurel%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jiaona%20Zhang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStanford%20lecturer%20Jiaona%20Zhang%20says%20every%20new%20grad%20should%20look%20for%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20workflows%26quot%3B%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20role%20she%20described%20involves%20implementing%20AI-optimization%20strategies%20within%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZhang%20said%20the%20role%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20new%20Biz%20Ops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBiz%20Ops%20jobs%20are%20so%20yesterday.%20Now%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20AI%20Ops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJiaona%20Zhang%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20for%20the%20AI%20time-keeping%20platform%20Laurel%2C%20which%20announced%20a%20%24100%20million%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20last%20year%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20though%20AI%20has%20been%20disrupting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-changing-entry-level-work-advice-to-succeed-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20role%20will%20become%20increasingly%20prevalent%20for%20new%20grads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20calls%20it%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20workflows%26quot%3B%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20involves%20identifying%20areas%20within%20an%20organization%20that%20could%20be%20optimized%20using%20AI%2C%20and%20then%20putting%20those%20changes%20into%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%2C%20who's%20also%20an%20adjunct%20lecturer%20in%20product%20management%20at%20Stanford%20and%20has%20worked%20at%20WeWork%2C%20Airbnb%2C%20and%20Dropbox%2C%20said%20the%20AI%20workflows%20role%20can%20be%20done%20across%20every%20department%20in%20a%20company.%20In%20sales%2C%20for%20example%2C%20an%20employee%20could%20identify%20and%20build%20automation%20solutions%20for%20cold%20emailing%20and%20demo%20calls.%20Zhang%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELaurel%20hired%20a%20new%20grad%20for%20this%20role%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edesign%20an%20agent%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20personal%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20the%20company's%20salespeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20most%20celebrated%20person%20at%20this%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20has%20since%20expanded%20their%20%26quot%3BAI%20Ops%26quot%3B%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20every%20company%20should%20be%20hiring%20for%20this%20AI%20workflows%20role.%20It's%20the%20new%20Biz%20Ops%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20the%20role%20I'd%20really%20push%20every%20single%20new%20grad%20to%20be%20going%20into.%26quot%3B%20Even%20though%20the%20role%20isn't%20all%20that%20common%20yet%2C%20she%20said%20graduates%20can%20create%20this%20role%20at%20the%20companies%20they%20work%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20work%20in%20sales%2C%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20automate%20workflows%20using%20AI%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20being%20the%20single%20salesperson%20hitting%20your%20quota%2C%20you're%20able%20to%20scale%20your%20impact%20across%20the%20entire%20sales%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20could%20start%20proving%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%20that%20you've%20saved%20a%20group%20of%20people%20this%20much%20time%20and%20you%20created%20this%20much%20leverage%2C%20that%20is%20the%20way%20to%20scream%20your%20worth%20to%20every%20employer%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20cloud%20company%20Box%20announced%20it%20was%20hiring%20for%20a%20similar-sounding%20role%2C%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbox-hiring-ai-business-automation-engineer-agent-role-palantir-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20business%20automation%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20up%20to%20%24183%2C000.%20Box's%20CEO%20said%20on%20X%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20role%20is%20%26quot%3Bakin%20to%20a%20forward-deployed%20engineer%20for%20internal%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20most%20companies%20will%20have%20many%20flavors%20of%20this%20going%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang's%20advice%20comes%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20AI%20transforms%20the%20way%20people%20work%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-ai-bad-bosses-replace-young-employees-chatgpt-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundercuts%20many%20entry-level%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leaving%20people%20across%20industries%20grappling%20with%20how%20to%20get%20ahead%20and%20how%20to%20AI-proof%20their%20jobs.%20Leaders%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-what-kids-should-study-ai-education-advice-2026-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Nvidia%2520chief%2520pointed%2520to%2Crespond%2520dynamically%2520in%2520the%2520moment.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-galloway-top-skills-ai-proofing-kids-careers-storytel