s%20De%20Cecco)%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E8%20ounces%20of%20small-diced%20pancetta%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20cup%20of%20shelled%20fresh%20peas%20or%20frozen%20peas%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BD%20pound%20of%20snow%20peas%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E12-14%20thin%20asparagus%20(bottom%20third%20discarded)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E5%20scallions%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BC%20cup%20of%20fresh%20chives%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20lemon%20(zest%20and%20juice)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BD%20cup%20of%20heavy%20cream%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20extra-large%20eggs%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20extra-large%20egg%20yolks%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%BE%20cup%20freshly%20grated%20Italian%20Parmesan%20cheese%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20Garten's%20pasta%20for%20three%20people%2C%20so%20I%20split%20these%20measurements%20in%20half%20while%20testing%20the%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20always%20finish%20my%20prep%20before%20I%20start%20cooking%2C%20an%20important%20lesson%20I%20learned%20the%20first%20time%20I%20made%20carbonara.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3b75e3457001926527a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20really%20get%20cooking%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-michelin-starred-spaghetti-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbonara%20pasta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20everything%20needs%20to%20be%20mixed%20very%20quickly%20to%20achieve%20maximum%20creaminess%20(and%20ensure%20you're%20not%20eating%20raw%20egg).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20sure%20I%20had%20every%20step%20prepped%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20stressed%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20put%20Garten's%20pasta%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%2C%20I%20cut%20my%20asparagus%20into%202-inch%20pieces%C2%A0and%20diagonally%20sliced%20my%20scallions%2C%20as%20her%20recipe%20instructed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20prepped%20the%20snow%20peas%2C%20chives%2C%20and%20lemon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3d0a412370019d319ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20lemon%20are%20required%20for%20different%20steps%2C%20I%20zested%20the%20lemon%20and%20then%20juiced%20it%20in%20a%20separate%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20julienned%20the%20snow%20peas%20and%20minced%20my%20chives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20last%20step%20of%20prep%20was%20filling%20a%20large%20bowl%20with%20hot%20tap%20water.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cda412370019d319aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20recommends%20using%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hottest%20tap%20water%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20heat%20the%20bowl%20you'll%20use%20to%20mix%20the%20pasta%20with%20the%20carbonara%20sauce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20her%20instructions%2C%20I%20set%20the%20full%20bowl%20aside%20while%20I%20cooked%20the%20pasta%20and%20pancetta.%20Garten%20says%20you%20should%20only%20pour%20the%20hot%20water%20out%20of%20the%20bowl%20%26quot%3Bjust%20before%20you%20drain%20the%20pasta.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20drizzled%20some%20olive%20oil%20into%20a%20saut%C3%A9%20pan%20over%20medium%20heat%20and%20added%20the%20pancetta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3b5a412370019d319a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20recommends%20stirring%20your%20pancetta%20occasionally%20and%20cooking%20until%20it's%20browned%2C%20which%20took%20about%20eight%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20your%20pancetta%20is%20ready%2C%20transfer%20it%20to%20a%20plate%20lined%20with%20a%20paper%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20my%20pancetta%20cooked%2C%20I%20started%20on%20my%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cb5e3457001926527f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20a%20large%20pot%20of%20salted%20water%20to%20a%20boil%2C%20then%20added%20my%20spaghetti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20cooked%20the%20pasta%20for%20eight%20minutes%2C%20stirring%20the%20noodles%20occasionally.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20saved%20a%20cup%20of%20the%20pasta%20water%20and%20then%20added%20some%20of%20the%20veggies.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3caa412370019d319a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221742%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20set%20the%20pasta%20water%20aside%20for%20the%20carbonara%20sauce%2C%20then%20threw%20in%20my%20snow%20peas%2C%20frozen%20peas%2C%20and%20asparagus%20with%20the%20spaghetti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20let%20everything%20cook%20together%20for%20two%20additional%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20prepped%20the%20carbonara%20sauce%20just%20before%20I%20drained%20my%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cba412370019d319a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dumped%20the%20hot%20tap%20water%20out%20of%20the%20bowl%2C%20then%20added%20the%20cream%2C%20egg%2C%20egg%20yolk%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20pasta%20water%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Garten%20recommends%20%C2%BC%20cup%20if%20you're%20making%20this%20dish%20for%20six%20%E2%80%94%20and%20whisked%20everything%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20my%20pasta%20was%20ready%2C%20I%20drained%20the%20spaghetti%20and%20veggies.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3ce5e34570019265281%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20time%20to%20turn%20this%20pasta%20into%20a%20spaghetti%20carbonara!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20added%20my%20noodles%20and%20veggies%20to%20the%20carbonara%20sauce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3ce5e34570019265282%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tossed%20everything%20together%20with%20tongs%2C%20making%20sure%20the%20spaghetti%20absorbed%20the%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20added%20another%20splash%20of%20pasta%20water%20to%20keep%20the%20sauce%20creamy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20I%20threw%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ingredients.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cfa412370019d319ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221605%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20added%20the%20Parmesan%20cheese%20to%20the%20pasta%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20pancetta%2C%20scallions%2C%20chives%2C%20lemon%20zest%2C%20and%20lemon%20juice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20seasoned%20everything%20with%20some%20salt%20and%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20tossing%20everything%20together%2C%20I%20admired%20the%20bright%20pasta%20dish.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cfa412370019d319ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20Garten%20loves%20making%20this%20dish%20in%20the%20spring.%20The%20green%20of%20the%20veggies%20and%20the%20red%20of%20the%20pancetta%20pop%20really%20nicely%20against%20the%20spaghetti%2C%20making%20the%20pasta%20look%20really%20fresh%20and%20inviting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20whip%20up%20a%20big%20serving%20of%20this%20dish%20in%20no%20time%20at%20all.%20Even%20though%20I%20split%20Garten's%20measurements%20in%20half%2C%20we%20still%20had%20more%20than%20enough%20food%20for%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20added%20some%20extra%20chives%20and%20Parmesan%20before%20serving%20the%20carbonara%2C%20which%20everyone%20loved.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Spring%20Carbonara%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60abd3cf5e34570019265284%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20little%20apprehensive%20of%20this%20dish%20when%20I%20first%20read%20the%20recipe%2C%20I%20won't%20lie.%20I'm%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20Garten's%20comforting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-ina-garten-easy-weeknight-bolognese-pasta-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered-sauce%20pastas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20her%20spring%20carbonara%20seemed%2C%20well%2C%20a%20little%20too%20%3Cem%3Egreen%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised!%20The%20carbonara%20sauce%20is%20creamy%20without%20feeling%20heavy%2C%20and%20it's%20balanced%20nicely%20with%20the%20fresh%20veggies.%20The%20pancetta%20also%20adds%20a%20lovely%20crunch%20and%20umami%20to%20the%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20wish%20there%20had%20been%20a%20bit%20more%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20served%20the%20dish%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20who%20both%20loved%20it.%20My%20dad%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Blight%20and%20lemony%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20my%20mom%20thought%20it'd%20be%20ideal%20for%20a%20barbecue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20never%20think%20to%20put%20all%20of%20these%20things%20together%2C%20but%20they%20tasted%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20light%20and%20refreshing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20some%20inspiration%20for%20a%20spring%20dinner%20party%20or%20weekend%20brunch%2C%20Garten's%20carbonara%20will%20definitely%20pack%20a%20punch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu