.%20Keeping%20that%20promise%20was%20incredibly%20hard.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man's%20hands%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b55d4abc4e9d88574b201%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFiordaliso%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJason%20Kidushim's%20grandfather%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Alzheimer's%20in%20his%2080s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20grandfather%20had%20a%20solid%20financial%20plan%20and%20could%20afford%20caregivers%2C%20but%20it%20was%20challenging.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJason%20founded%20a%20company%20to%20coordinate%20home%20care%2C%20and%20has%20worked%20with%204%2C000%20families%20since.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EJason%20Kidushim%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Legacy%20Concierge.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%2C%20Joseph%2C%20was%20a%20proud%2C%20amazing%20man.%20He%20was%20a%20decorated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-9-greatest-war-hero-presidents-of-the-united-states-2014-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20hero%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20lost%20a%20leg%20helping%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20other%20service%20members%20during%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20never%20slowed%20him%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20he%20would%20show%20off%20his%20stump.%20He'd%20dive%20off%20the%20diving%20board%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-explain-why-people-feel-better-near-the-ocean-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswim%20in%20the%20ocean%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20him%20as%20disabled%20or%20handicapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20a%20senior%20in%20high%20school%2C%20my%20grandfather%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falzheimers-and-dementia-misconceptions-and-surprising-facts-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediagnosed%20with%20Alzheimer's%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20first%20five%20or%20so%20years%2C%20not%20much%20changed.%20He%20continued%20to%20live%20at%20home%20with%20my%20grandmother.%20Then%2C%20when%20she%20died%2C%20my%20grandfather%20moved%20in%20with%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20my%20dad%20promise%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20go%20into%20a%20facility.%20He%20had%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20hospitals%20during%20his%20time%20in%20the%20service%2C%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20die%20in%20one.%20My%20parents%20were%20able%20to%20honor%20that%20promise%2C%20and%20my%20grandfather%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-died-at-home-family-still-lives-there-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edied%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20keeping%20that%20vow%20was%20a%20logistical%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227522ab49-eeb3-4d01-89dd-ffaafd7f212b%5C%22%3EI%20saw%20the%20strain%20of%20caretaking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20right%20in%20caring%20for%20my%20grandfather.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20still%20wasn't%20enough.%20There%20were%20some%20really%2C%20really%20difficult%20moments%20and%20dynamics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20photo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b5978abc4e9d88574b225%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Kidushim%20started%20his%20company%20after%20seeing%20the%20strain%20his%20parents%20went%20through%20taking%20care%20of%20his%20grandfather.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Kidushim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandfather%20and%20father%20sold%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fis-life-insurance-a-good-investment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helped%20many%20people%20with%20estate%20planning.%20Having%20a%20financial%20plan%20in%20place%20was%20very%20helpful%20when%20my%20grandfather%20got%20sick.%20We%20were%20also%20able%20to%20get%20my%20grandfather%20into%20an%20outstanding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-attends-free-adult-day-care-low-income-no-savings-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadult%20day%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Being%20there%20really%20prolonged%20his%20happiness%20and%20gave%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20toll%20that%20caregiving%20took.%20My%20mother%20had%20only%20just%20finished%20raising%20her%20three%20kids%20when%20my%20grandfather%20moved%20in.%20Caring%20for%20him%20was%20important%20work%2C%20and%20she%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Frising-sandwich-generation-reshapes-workforce-dynamics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evolunteers%20with%20hospice%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20because%20it%20was%20so%20meaningful%20to%20her.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20was%20really%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20coordinating%20logistics.%20He%20was%20the%20one%20hiring%2C%20scheduling%2C%20and%20paying%20my%20grandfather's%20caregivers%2C%20which%20was%20a%20job%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd0a3d4e-dc74-4b3c-ad41-941b5ec02850%5C%22%3ECare%20costs%20can%20be%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20per%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20don't%20realize%20how%20complicated%20organizing%20home%20care%20is.%20It's%20not%20only%20about%20finding%20kind%2C%20qualified%20helpers%20%E2%80%94%20you%20also%20need%20to%20understand%20labor%20laws%20and%20plan%20for%20things%20like%20workers'%20compensation%2C%20phone%20reimbursements%2C%20and%20overtime%20pay.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20details%20that%20can%20trip%20you%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20hugely%20expensive.%20When%20you%20factor%20in%20workers'%20comp%20and%20benefits%2C%20people%20here%20in%20California%20can%20expect%20to%20pay%20%2432%20to%20%2460%20per%20hour%20for%20a%20nonmedical%20caregiver%2C%20and%20about%20%24125%20to%204300%20per%20hour%20for%20a%20nurse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20grandfather's%20death%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegacyconcierge.com%2Fpages%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efounded%20a%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20handles%20the%20details%20for%20coordinating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-healthcare-startup-navi-nurses-growth-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecare%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20medical%20and%20nonmedical%20caregiving.%20Since%20founding%20the%20company%2C%20I've%20worked%20with%20probably%204%2C000%20families.%20It's%20amazing%20how%20different%20each%20one%20is.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20factors%20that%20impact%20end-of-life%20care%2C%20whether%20it's%20money%20(or%20lack%20of%20it)%20or%20relationships%20between%20the%20elderly%20and%20their%20grown%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22622ad668-c397-4f26-9e6b-77210bd899a7%5C%22%3EIt's%20still%20hard%20to%20talk%20with%20my%20parents%20about%20end%20of%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20my%20personal%20and%20professional%20experience%20coordinating%20care%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20it's%20still%20hard%20to%20talk%20about%20with%20my%20own%20parents%2C%20who%20are%20in%20their%2060s.%20My%20parents%20both%20have%20long-term%20care%20insurance%2C%20which%20provides%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20year%2C%20I%20try%20to%20talk%20with%20them%20about%20the%20harder%20questions%20%E2%80%94%20like%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20they%20were%20put%20on%20a%20ventilator.%20These%20are%20not%20very%20fun%20conversations%20to%20have%2C%20but%20they%20take%20the%20guesswork%20out%20of%20things%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20wants%20to%20think%20about%20needing%20a%20caretaker%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20put%20these%20conversations%20on%20the%20back%20burner%20until%20there's%20a%20catastrophe.%20But%20if%20you%20can%20educate%20yourself%20about%20options%20and%20put%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20for%20end-of-life%20care%2C%20things%20will%20be%20so%20much%20easier%20when%20you%20need%20to%20activate%20that%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaring-for-grandfather-alzheimers-at-home-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779798901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b5712abc4e9d88574b20c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaring-for-grandfather-alzheimers-at-home-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jason%20Kidushim%20says%20caring%20for%20his%20grandfather%20with%20Alzheimer's%20revealed%20the%20emotional%20and%20financial%20strain%20of%20home%20caregiving.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quad%20launches%20Indo-Pacific%20energy%20security%20framework%20amid%20Hormuz%20crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779798871000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131329752%2Cimgsize-1115781.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Funinterrupted-flow-of-global-commerce-quad-launches-indo-pacific-energy-security-framework-amid-hormuz-crisis%2Farticleshow%2F131329617.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Quad%20nations%20have%20launched%20a%20new%20energy%20security%20framework%20for%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20focusing%20on%20strategic%20fuel%20reserves%20and%20emergency%20response%20to%20counter%20supply%20disruptions.%20This%20initiative%2C%20announced%20after%20a%20m