s%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20asked%20over%20200%20travelers%20to%20share%20their%20biggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-american-made-first-visit-japan-regrets-2025-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJapan%20travel%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20found%20clear%20patterns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECommon%20issues%20included%20overplanning%2C%20navigating%20public%20transport%2C%20and%20having%20too-high%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETheir%20advice%20consistently%20pointed%20to%20the%20same%20tips%3A%20slow%20down%2C%20plan%20less%2C%20and%20leave%20space%20for%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok%20feed%20looks%20anything%20like%20mine%2C%20it%20probably%20feels%20like%20everyone%20is%20either%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Kyoto%2C%20or%20has%20just%20come%20back%20from%20Japan.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-planning-mistakes-japan-american-made-first-trip-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20around%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20and%2C%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20I've%20called%20Kobe%20home.%20Recently%2C%20I%20asked%20The%20Navigatio's%20Japan%20Travel%20Tips%20%26amp%3B%20Planning%20group%20on%20Facebook%20one%20simple%20question%3A%20What%20was%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-first-trip-to-japan-how-to-avoid-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20Japan%20travel%20mistake%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20900%2C000%20members%2C%20more%20than%20200%20answered.%20Here%20are%20my%20biggest%20takeaways%20based%20on%20their%20responses%2C%20plus%20some%20of%20my%20own%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20planned%20their%20trip%20around%20viral%20content%20instead%20of%20their%20own%20interests.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arashiyama%20Bamboo%20Forest%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1075227ff506e273e66977%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Eleochen66%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERepeatedly%2C%20people%20said%20they%20regretted%20building%20itineraries%20around%20viral%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20posts%20instead%20of%20their%20own%20interests.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-most-instagrammed-countries-in-the-world-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20Instagrammed%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20curated%20images%20of%20empty%20bamboo%20forests%20and%20quiet%20shrine%20paths%20rarely%20match%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20commented%20that%20they%20planned%20their%20entire%20trips%20around%20famous%20spots%20like%20Fushimi%20Inari%20Taisha%20or%20Arashiyama%20Bamboo%20Grove%2C%20only%20to%20find%20themselves%20waking%20up%20at%204%3A30%20a.m.%20to%20chase%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20photo%26quot%3B%20alongside%20hundreds%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20stood%20out%20most%20was%20how%20often%20people%20told%20me%20they%20valued%20unplanned%20moments%20more%20than%20scheduled%20ones.%20As%20one%20traveler%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20stopped%20following%20every%20recommendation%20and%20just%20explored.%20It%20was%20a%20much%20better%20trip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20visiting%20Japan's%20iconic%20sights%2C%20but%20the%20best%20trips%20happen%20when%20they're%20only%20part%20of%20the%20itinerary.%20Build%20a%20trip%20around%20your%20own%20interests%2C%20not%20what's%20trending%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20travelers%20regretted%20overpacking%20their%20itineraries.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alley%20in%20Kyoto%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a107642b1025a62a5c86155%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20travelers%20only%20spend%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20Kyoto%20when%20they%20wish%20they'd%20spent%20several%20days%20there.%3Cp%3EFrancesco%20Riccardo%20Iacomino%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20a%20way%20of%20making%20people%20overly%20ambitious.%20You%20land%20in%20Tokyo%20and%20suddenly%20convince%20yourself%20you%20can%20fit%20Kyoto%2C%20Osaka%2C%20Nara%2C%20and%20Hiroshima%20into%20a%20single%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20travelers%20told%20me%20they%20regretted%20overpacking%20their%20itineraries%20and%2C%20by%20trying%20to%20visit%20too%20many%20cities%20in%20one%20trip%2C%20they%20didn't%20spend%20enough%20time%20in%20any%20of%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20what%20you%20actually%20want%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-part-japan-trip-hakone-things-to-do-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20completely%20change%20the%20way%20you%20experience%20it%20once%20you%20arrive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20rest%20and%20recharge%2C%20a%20mountain%20onsen%20ryokan%20in%20Arima%20Onsen%20or%20Kusatsu%20Onsen%20is%20a%20great%20choice.%20For%20culture%2C%20food%2C%20and%20nightlife%2C%20a%20base%20like%20Fukuoka%20can%20offer%20you%20variety%2C%20with%20easy%20access%20to%20day%20trips%20around%20Kyushu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20isn't%20going%20anywhere%2C%20and%20many%20people%20said%20their%20best%20trips%20came%20on%20return%20visits%2C%20once%20the%20pressure%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20Japan%20properly%26quot%3B%20had%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20got%20caught%20up%20in%20Japan's%20transport%20system.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20trains%20in%20Japan%20and%20bridges%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1079ff51ede568c7e177a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EChamphei%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20easy%20to%20get%20around%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20efficient%20trains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20you%20arrive%20at%20places%20like%20Shinjuku%20Station%20with%20its%20200%20exits%20and%20layered%20underground%20walkways%2C%20you'll%20quickly%20realize%20that's%20not%20entirely%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20efficient%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-bullet-train-first-time-shinkansen-pros-cons-osaka-tokyo-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJapan's%20train%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20always%20intuitive%20to%20navigate%20at%20first.%20Living%20here%20without%20a%20car%2C%20I've%20relied%20entirely%20on%20trains%20and%20still%20occasionally%20miss%20stops%20or%20fumble%20scanning%20QR%20codes%20at%20ticket%20gates%20(quick%20tip%3A%20turn%20your%20screen%20brightness%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20travelers%20also%20told%20me%20they%20regret%20buying%20the%20JR%20pass%2C%20a%20once-popular%20option%20for%20multicity%20travel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESignificant%20price%20increases%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20changed%20the%20rail%20pass's%20value%2C%20and%20many%20commenters%20admitted%20they%20bought%20it%20out%20of%20habit%20without%20checking%20whether%20it%20would%20actually%20save%20them%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20still%20be%20worthwhile%20for%20some%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20crunching%20some%20numbers%20based%20on%20your%20itinerary%20before%20deciding%20whether%20to%20purchase%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20to%20save%20time%20and%20reduce%20the%20stress%20of%20navigating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-japan-biggest-surprises-food-culture-money-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJapan's%20public%20transport%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20use%20taxis%20where%20possible%2C%20especially%20in%20cities%20like%20Kyoto%2C%20where%20buses%20can%20get%20crowded%20and%20move%20slowly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENo%20one%20seemed%20prepared%20for%20the%20amount%20of%20walking%20they'd%20be%20doing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20tourists%20and%20locals%20cross%20the%20steep%2C%20arched%20wooden%20spans%20of%20the%20historic%20Kintai%20Bridge%20(Kintaikyo)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10768c7ff506e273e6699a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMake%20sure%20you%20have%20comfortable%20shoes%20on%20if%20you're%20walking%20the%20historic%20Kintai%20Bridge.%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20commenter%20mentioned%20they%20didn't%20expect%20to%20walk%2015%2C000%20to%2025%2C000%20steps%20a%20day%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20very%20sore%20feet%20by%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20Japan%20has%20plenty%20of%20hills%2C%20stairs%2C%20and%20steep%20shrine%20approaches%20that%20appear%20in%20almost%20every%20outing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20few%20experienced%20travelers%20wrote%20that%20they%20were%20surprised%20by%20the%20physical%20demands%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20hotter%20months%20of%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20comfortable%20footwear%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20repeated%20pieces%20of%20advice%20in%20the%20comments%2C%20along%20with%20keeping%20daily%20itineraries%20lighter%20and%20more%20realistic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20ask%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-packing-list-round-the-world-trip-travel-essentials-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat%20to%20pack%20for%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20always%20recommend%20comfortable%20walking%20shoes%20first.%20Staying%20in%20accommodations%20near%20train%20stations%20and%20leaving%20room%20for%20breaks%20between%20activities%20can%20also%20make%20a%20trip%20less%20exhausting%20and%20much%20more%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20planned%20around%20expectations%20instead%20of%20reality%20(and%20the%20season).%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boat%20sailing%20past%20cherry%20blossom%20trees%20in%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1076b7b1025a62a5c86160%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPhotography%20by%20ZhangXun%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20first-time%20visitors%20dream%20of%20visiting%20Japan%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisiting-japan-for-cherry-blossom-season-tips-from-local-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echerry-blossom%20season%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Although%20it%20can%20look%20dreamy%20online%2C%20as%20costs%20surge%20and%20popular%20viewing%20spots%20become%20tightly%20packed%2C%20the%20experience%20can%20feel%20more%20like%20navigating%20crowds%20with%20flowers%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20writers%20who%20told%20me%20they%20visited%20during%20this%20season%20said%20the%20views%20were%20beautiful%2C%20but%20all%20the%20people%20and%20higher%20prices%20put%20a%20slight%20damper%20on%20their%20trip.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20cherry-blossom%20season%2C%20many%20said%20they%20felt%20disappointed%20when%20real-life%20conditions%20didn't%20match%20what%20they%20had%20seen%20online.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-condo-demolished-blocking-mount-fuji-view-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMount%20Fuji%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20good%20example.%20On%20social%20media%2C%20it%20is%20often%20presented%20as%20a%20guaranteed%20view%20from%20places%20like%20Hakone%20or%20Kawaguchiko%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20it's%20