0symbols%20and%20motifs%2C%20such%20as%20bows%20and%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20dainty%20flowers%2C%20Sharpe%20suggests%20finding%20heirloom%20charms%20or%20a%20symbol%20that%20resonates%20with%20someone's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20it%20more%20intentional%2C%20like%20your%20initial%20or%20something%20that%20actually%20speaks%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharpe%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-jewelry-right-now-summer-trends-jewelers-stylists-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779796021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04a4d458810e27922ad431%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-jewelry-right-now-summer-trends-jewelers-stylists-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jewelers%20and%20stylists%20said%20pearls%20and%20cocktail%20rings%20are%20in%20this%20summer.%20However%2C%20dainty%20jewelry%20and%20logo-heavy%20pieces%20are%20becoming%20less%20popular.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Cheyenne%20Elwell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Too%20hot%20to%20think%3A%20How%20heatwaves%20are%20affecting%20children%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20learning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779795930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131329268%2Cimgsize-58310.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Ftoo-hot-to-think-how-heatwaves-are-affecting-childrens-health-and-learning%2Farticleshow%2F131328072.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20grapples%20with%20severe%20heatwaves%2C%20impacting%20children's%20health%20and%20education.%20Experts%20highlight%20children's%20vulnerability%20to%20heat%2C%20urging%20pare