iation%20regulators%20are%20concerned%20about%20power%20banks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20passenger's%20mistake%20while%20packing%20their%20luggage%20forced%20their%20flight%20to%20be%20diverted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20latest%20case%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-power-banks-crack-down-rules-lithium-batteries-how-safe-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20upending%20travelers'%20plans%2C%20as%20aviation%20regulators%20call%20for%20increased%20awareness%20of%20the%20devices'%20potential%20hazards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20passenger%20on%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-easyjet-wizz-europes-budget-airlines-compared-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EeasyJet%20flight%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Etold%20the%20crew%20during%20the%20flight%20that%20a%20power%20bank%20was%20charging%20a%20device%20in%20their%20checked%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20from%20Hurghada%2C%20Egypt%2C%20to%20London%20diverted%20to%20Rome%20because%20regulations%20state%20that%20power%20banks%20are%20not%20allowed%20in%20the%20airplane's%20cargo%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassengers%20then%20had%20to%20wait%20overnight%20to%20continue%20their%20journey%20after%20the%20Airbus%20A320%20landed%20in%20the%20Italian%20capital%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20landed%20safely%20and%20passengers%20disembarked%20routinely%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20easyJet%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provided%20hotel%20accommodation%20and%20meals%20where%20available%20and%20provided%20customers%20who%20stayed%20in%20the%20airport%20with%20refreshments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fm7TIW%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20of%20Europe%20and%20Africa%20shows%20the%20flight%20path%20of%20EasyJet%20flight%202618%20from%20Hurghada%20to%20London%20Luton%2C%20which%20diverted%20to%20Rome.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fm7TIW%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20reached%20London%20Luton%20Airport%20around%204%20p.m.%20the%20next%20day%2C%20nearly%2016%20hours%20later%20than%20it%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20sorry%20for%20any%20inconvenience%20caused%20by%20the%20diversion%20and%20subsequent%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20easyJet%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPower%20banks%20can%20only%20be%20carried%20in%20an%20airplane's%20cabin%20because%20they%20pose%20a%20fire%20risk%20due%20to%20their%20lithium%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLithium%20batteries%20power%20lots%20of%20everyday%20electronics%2C%20from%20vapes%20and%20mobile%20phones%20to%20cameras%20and%20power%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Glenn%20Bradley%2C%20the%20UK%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority's%20head%20of%20flight%20operations%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20become%20faulty%20or%20damaged%2C%20they%20can%20cause%20an%20intense%20fire%20that%20is%20difficult%20to%20extinguish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20due%20to%20a%20process%20called%20thermal%20runaway%2C%20which%20sparks%20a%20chain%20reaction%20and%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20temperature.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20easyJet%20incident%2C%20the%20CAA%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20awareness%26quot%3B%20was%20needed%20as%20portable%20chargers%20carry%20%26quot%3Bserious%20risks%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattery-fire-airlines-aviation-safety-power-banks-sas-faa-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverheating%20or%20catching%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20passenger%20who%20packed%20it%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%20and%20ended%20up%20with%20all%20the%20other%20passengers%20in%20the%20wrong%20city%20because%20the%20flight%20was%20diverted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CAA's%20Jonathan%20Nicholson%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20are%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20power%20banks%20since%20the%20growing%20market%20for%20the%20devices%20means%20that%20many%20are%20cheaply%20made%20and%20not%20properly%20certified.%20They%20may%20also%20lack%20the%20advanced%20circuitry%20that%20helps%20stop%20laptops%20and%20phones%20from%20overcharging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20airlines%20also%20say%20that%20power%20banks%20cannot%20be%20used%20on%20board.%20It%20is%20safest%20to%20ensure%20devices%20are%20kept%20visible%20and%20accessible.%20This%20means%20that%20smoke%20or%20a%20fire%20can%20be%20spotted%20more%20quickly%20than%20if%20the%20device%20were%20in%20an%20overhead%20bin.%20Airline%20crews%20are%20well-trained%20in%20dealing%20with%20electrical%20fires%2C%20so%20they%20can%20react%20promptly%20if%20anything%20goes%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20carriers%20introduced%20stricter%20rules%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20an%20overhead%20bin%20in%20Busan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20in%20January%202025%2C%20the%20country's%20transport%20ministry%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-power-banks-fire-diversion-lithium-battery-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eban%20on%20storing%20power%20banks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20e-cigarettes%20in%20the%20overhead%20bins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%20prohibited%20passengers%20from%20charging%20devices%20with%20power%20banks%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-day-after-new-rules-for-portable-chargers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20mandated%20that%20they%20cannot%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20bag%20or%20overhead%20bin%20while%20in%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFlying%20is%20by%20far%20the%20safest%20way%20to%20travel%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20it%20that%20way.%20Packing%20safely%20reduces%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20battery-powered%20items%20with%20you%20will%20make%20your%20flight%20safer%20for%20you%2C%20and%20the%20other%20passengers%20you're%20flying%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassengers-power-bank-mishap-brings-aviation-safety-into-focus-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779793118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1577b651ede568c7e188db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassengers-power-bank-mishap-brings-aviation-safety-into-focus-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22EasyJet%20passengers%20had%20to%20wait%20overnight%20after%20their%20flight%20diverted%20when%20a%20passenger%20told%20crew%20their%20power%20bank%20was%20charging%20in%20their%20checked%20bag.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40businessinsider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hidden%20reason%20plane%20windows%20have%20tiny%20holes%3A%20What%20travellers%20should%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779792542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131327449%2Cimgsize-44512.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Ftravel%2Fnews%2Fthe-hidden-reason-plane-windows-have-tiny-holes-what-travellers-should-know-before-their-next-flight%2Farticleshow%2F131327313.cm