0have%20died%20after%20an%20overpass%20partially%20collapsed%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsouth-korea-overpass-collapse-kills-three-13548125%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20the%20IPO%20boom%20a%202021%20repeat%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228151%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22spacex%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10d1b551ede568c7e17dc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225437%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpaceX%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20are%20set%20for%20major%20IPOs%2C%20raising%20investor%20excitement%20for%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20is%20the%20IPO%20hype%20too%20reminiscent%20of%20periods%20like%202021%20and%201999%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBy%20proceeds%20raised%2C%202026%20could%20take%20the%20cake%20for%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20year%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20lots%20of%20chatter%20in%20recent%20weeks%20about%20the%20mega%20IPOs%20expected%20to%20come%20to%20market%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20first%20among%20them%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-filing-going-public-investors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20go%20public%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20a%20movie%20we've%20seen%20before%3F%20The%20last%20time%20there%20was%20this%20much%20hype%20around%20IPOs%20was%20during%20the%202021%20SPAC%20boom.%20With%20the%20economy%20flush%20with%20cash%2C%20the%20high%20number%20of%20companies%20going%20public%20was%20one%20symptom%20of%20insatiable%20investor%20demand.%20The%20euphoria%20didn't%20last%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20falling%20as%20much%20as%2025%25%20to%20kick%20off%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%20there%20was%20the%20surge%20of%20IPOs%20in%201999%2C%20as%20companies%20sought%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20market's%20enthusiasm%20about%20an%20emerging%20technology%20in%20the%20internet.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20the%20market%20began%20a%20multi-year%20meltdown%20now%20known%20as%20the%20dot-com%20bust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20investors%20are%20eager%20to%20get%20into%20expected%20IPOs%20from%20SpaceX%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ipo-racing-to-go-public-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Anthropic.%20How%20worried%20should%20we%20be%20that%20this%20is%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20over-exuberance%20destined%20to%20end%20like%20past%20market%20frenzies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20perfect%20comparison%20in%20markets%2C%20but%20let's%20examine%20some%20of%20the%20similarities%20and%20differences%20between%20now%20and%20then%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBy%20sheer%20number%20of%20IPOs%20coming%20to%20market%2C%202026%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20be%20as%20hot%20as%201999%20or%202021.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20expects%20to%20see%20100%20IPOs%20this%20year%2C%20while%201999%20and%202021%20saw%20457%20and%201%2C035%20launches%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20Reflexivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoing%20by%20proceeds%20raised%2C%20however%2C%202026%20could%20take%20the%20cake.%20According%20to%20Morningstar%2C%20the%20IPOs%20of%20SpaceX%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-anthropic-paying-ai-compute-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20would%20all%20break%20previous%20records%20for%20venture-capital-backed%20IPOs.%20%26quot%3BTogether%20they%20could%20raise%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20in%20proceeds%20and%20generate%20a%20total%20exit%20value%20higher%20than%20all%20US%20VC-backed%20IPOs%20since%202000%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20wrote%20in%20March.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20per%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Michael%20Hartnett%2C%20the%20top%2010%20AI%20stocks%20currently%20account%20for%20around%2040%25%20of%20total%20market%20capitalization.%20Coming%20IPOs%20will%20push%20that%20group%20to%20around%2050%25%20of%20the%20market.%20That%20would%20be%20more%20than%20any%20other%20period%20in%20history%2C%20except%20for%20the%20railroad%20bubble%20in%20the%201880s%2C%20when%20the%20industry%20made%20up%2063%25%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELooking%20at%20broader%20market%20valuations%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-shiller-pe-ratio-dot-com-bubble-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500's%20Shiller%20CAPE%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2041%20is%20above%202021's%20levels%20and%20just%20below%20all-time%20highs%20seen%20in%202000.%20These%20IPOs%20could%20further%20exacerbate%20stock%20valuations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20market%20pros%20that%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Friday%2C%20today's%20IPO%20environment%20rhymes%20more%20with%201999%20than%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that%20it%20reminds%20us%20about%20is%20that%20the%20valuations%20in%20'99%20were%20just%20bonkers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-sp500-lost-decade-stock-market-investing-strategy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMolly%20Pieroni%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20president%20at%20Yacktman%20Asset%20Management%2C%20adding%20that%20SpaceX's%20valuation%20at%20150x%20revenue%20means%20it's%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20have%20to%20double%20revenue%20every%20year%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years%20to%20justify%20those%20kinds%20of%20valuations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValuations%20aside%2C%20however%2C%20Pieroni%20and%20others%20said%20that%20the%20large%20firms%20expected%20to%20go%20public%20this%20year%20are%20more%20solid%20businesses%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20long-term%20prospects%20and%20the%20revenue%20they're%20already%20generating%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it's%20not%20a%20flush%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Schiffer%2C%20founder%20of%20a%20family%20office%20called%20The%20Patriarch%20Organization%2C%20said%20that%20while%20investors%20should%20remain%20vigilant%20amid%20high%20valuations%2C%20the%20market%20is%20likely%20to%20go%20higher%20from%20here%20as%20he%20expects%20the%20Iran%20war%20to%20wrap%20up%2C%20ending%20an%20ongoing%20inflation%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20above%20all%20else%2C%20earnings%20continue%20to%20exceed%20expectations%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20earnings%20drive%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fipo-boom-spacex-openai-anthropic-2021-spac-1999-internet-repeat-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779789061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a10d1fe7ff506e273e66ff2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fipo-boom-spacex-openai-anthropic-2021-spac-1999-internet-repeat-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Is%20this%20a%20movie%20we've%20seen%20before%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russell%20Crowe%20Warns%20Crowd%20of%20Autograph-Seekers%20in%20Paris%20Not%20to%20Push%3A%20%E2%80%98As%20Soon%20as%20Somebody%E2%80%99s%20a%20D%E2%80%93k%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20Going%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779788898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236758711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russell%20Crowe%20gave%20fans%20a%20warning%20before%20signing%20autographs%20outside%20of%20his%20hotel%20in%20P